item.description:
Do you have any new books to share? What have you attracted/manifested since our last discussion? Join us for conversation and connection from 10:00a.m.-11:30a.m. We will meet outside if it's sunny and warm.

If you respond yes and find you can no longer attend, please change your response in order to create space for someone else to join us. Looking forward to seeing everyone.

Thank you!
item.how_to_find_us: Meet us in the back room, just beyond the soda station, table straight ahead
